:611.2pt;border-top-color:#000000;border-bottom-style:solid"><h5 id="h.247svd1nybjm" style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;page-break-after:avoid;margin-right:48pt;margin-left:-2.2pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;height:11pt;text-align:right"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:6pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></h5></td></tr><tr style="height:45pt"><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-right-style:solid;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;border-bottom-color:#00a797;border-top-width:1pt;border-right-width:1pt;border-left-color:#00a797;vertical-align:top;border-right-color:#00a797;border-left-width:1pt;border-top-style:solid;background-color:#00a797;border-left-style:solid;border-bottom-width:1pt;width:449.2pt;border-top-color:#00a797;border-bottom-style:solid"><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#fff9ed;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-right-style:solid;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;border-bottom-color:#00a797;border-top-width:1pt;border-right-width:1pt;border-left-color:#00a797;vertical-align:middle;border-right-color:#00a797;border-left-width:1pt;border-top-style:solid;background-color:#00a797;border-left-style:solid;border-bottom-width:1pt;width:162pt;border-top-color:#00a797;border-bottom-style:solid"><p style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:center"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p></td></tr></table><h6 id="h.k2z3n45ztaex" style="padding-top:10pt;color:#666666;padding-left:0;font-size:6pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.0;page-break-after:avoid;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:6pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#666666;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:6pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></h6></div><p style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;">Welcoming anti-Oedipus Welcoming anti-OOP-dipusintroductionCool. So, we&#39;re going to continue the transcript. Now, what I&#39;m going to do is uh read it out again. Um this is the um key script going forward. Uh you are going whenever I paste um this transcript, into you. You will um interpret it and and put it in um and to your edipass the language. and presentation. Um that&#39;s your job. My job is to supply the meanings and whimsy and and stuff based on the logic and the facts that we&#39;ve built together. Okay. Introduction. On the prohibition and the refusal of genealogical machines. Uh let&#39;s rewrite this. Um uh the book is called Anti-Oedipus. We will start um with the introduction. We will not write the introduction now. Uh by introduction I mean preface. The the Foucault written preface. We&#39;ll do that much later. I will skip ahead to the first Deleuze and Guattari chapter. Um in our own way. Uh okay.on the shutting machines. on the shit machines. I yes. There are shit machines. There are shitting machines. Shitting machines do not need to be shit machines. There can be shit shutting machines.BIOLOGY</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;PERIOD 1 </span></p><p style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal">MS. WENDY WRITER</span></p><p class="title" id="h.g6nr81xnwjj7" style="padding-top:16pt;color:#00a797;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:36pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span>K</span><span>ELLS<br></span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:36pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal">BASIC UNITS OF:</span></p><p class="title" id="h.ej52h9867dz0" style="padding-top:16pt;color:#00a797;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:36pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:71.2pt;text-indent:0.8pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:36pt;font-family:&quot;Old Standard TT&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Logic</span></p><p style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-weight:700;font-family:&quo