ont-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Welcoming Anti-&OElig;dipus.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Welcoming Anti-O^O.P.-dipus.</span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">On the prohibition and the refusal of genealogical machines.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">h okay.on the sh</span><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;">i</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">tting.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">on the shit machines.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;">&nbsp;&#256;e, </span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">yes.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">There are shit machines.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">There are shitting machines.</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Shitting machines do not need to b</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">: shit machine</span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="font-size:8pt;font-family:&quot;IBM Plex Mono&quot;;font-style:italic;font-weight:400">Shitting machines do not need to be shit machines. The flow-state permits the meta-function: There can be shit shitting machines. A tautology of the production/product-cycle.</span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;font-style:normal">There is one law that I know. Only one I can state as truth. &nbsp;</span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span>It is my most precious stone and I present it as </span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;font-style:normal">taonga.</span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:11pt;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><p style="padding-top:10pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.3;margin-right:-0.8pt;margin-left:-0.8pt;font-family:&quot;PT Serif&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-
